          "t": "p",
          "text": "About The Client"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Alibaba"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Daraz is the leading e-commerce platform across South Asia. After their advent as an online fashion retailer in 2012, they quickly expanded their business portfolio to a comprehensive online marketplace by 2015 and in 2018, they made a big move by becoming part of Alibaba’s expansive global footprint that enabled them to utilize Alibaba’s expertise in technology, logistics, and digital payments. Today, their platform proudly house 30 million active shoppers, supporting transactions for more than 200,000 active sellers and over 100,000 branded/non-branded products to sell."
        },
        {
          "t": "img",
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/alibaba-reb6f6fzc4hlu2h7ade0aw7bjk4loalc3at220tols.webp",
          "w": 200,
          "h": 200,
          "alt": "alibaba"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "2012 - Pakistan"
