    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "OUR SOLUTION"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Optimized Power BI Reporting"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 partnered with Alibaba to build a high-performance reporting solution using Microsoft Power BI. The approach was mainly focused on implementing advanced performance optimization techniques catering Alibaba’s large and complex dataset environment. The key aspects of our solution were:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Deep Data Model"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "We designed Alibaba’s Power BI data models to cater huge data volumes efficiently, reducing redundant calculations and boosting data retrieval speeds."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Advanced DAX Query Tuning"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Our Power BI experts refined Data Analysis Expressions (DAX) queries, turning complicated calculations into highly efficient formulas that processed data faster with more reliability."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Strategic Data Integration"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "We optimized data integration from Alibaba’s various data source systems to Power BI to maintain data integrity and freshness."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "EXPLORE OUR ECOMMERCE DATA SOLUTIONS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
